annotationA: 26S proteasome non-ATPase regulatory subunit 9; Acts as a chaperone during the assembly of the 26S proteasome, specifically of the base subcomplex of the PA700/19S regulatory complex (RC)
annotationB: 26S proteasome regulatory complex subunit p39A; Endopeptidase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: proteolysis; proteasome-mediated ubiquitin-dependent protein catabolic process; regulation of exit from mitosis
